{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.1","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:1","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.003.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Miracles d\u2019\u00c9lis\u00e9e. L\u2019huile de la veuve<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. 1 R 17:8-16. Mc 6:34-44. Ps 68:6. Ph 4:19.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Une femme d\u2019entre les femmes des fils des proph\u00e8tes cria \u00e0 \u00c9lis\u00e9e, en disant: Ton serviteur mon mari est mort, et tu sais que ton serviteur craignait l\u2019\u00c9ternel; or le cr\u00e9ancier est venu pour prendre mes deux enfants et en faire ses esclaves.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.2","name":"2 Rois 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.27","name":"2 Rois 3:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.3.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.2","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:2","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e lui dit: Que puis-je faire pour toi? Dis-moi, qu\u2019as-tu \u00e0 la maison? Elle r\u00e9pondit: Ta servante n\u2019a rien du tout \u00e0 la maison qu\u2019un vase d\u2019huile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.3","name":"2 Rois 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.1","name":"2 Rois 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.3","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:3","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et il dit: Va demander au-dehors des vases chez tous tes voisins, des vases vides, et n\u2019en demande pas un petit nombre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.4","name":"2 Rois 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.2","name":"2 Rois 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.4","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:4","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Quand tu seras rentr\u00e9e, tu fermeras la porte sur toi et sur tes enfants; tu verseras dans tous ces vases, et tu mettras de c\u00f4t\u00e9 ceux qui seront pleins.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.5","name":"2 Rois 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.3","name":"2 Rois 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.5","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:5","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Alors elle le quitta. Elle ferma la porte sur elle et sur ses enfants; ils lui pr\u00e9sentaient les vases, et elle versait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.6","name":"2 Rois 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.4","name":"2 Rois 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.6","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:6","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Lorsque les vases furent pleins, elle dit \u00e0 son fils: Pr\u00e9sente-moi encore un vase. Mais il lui r\u00e9pondit: Il n\u2019y a plus de vase. Et l\u2019huile s\u2019arr\u00eata.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.7","name":"2 Rois 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.5","name":"2 Rois 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.7","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:7","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Elle alla le rapporter \u00e0 l\u2019homme de Dieu, et il dit: Va vendre l\u2019huile, et paie ta dette; et tu vivras, toi et tes fils, de ce qui restera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.8","name":"2 Rois 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.6","name":"2 Rois 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.8","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:8","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le fils de la Sunamite<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-37: cf. (H\u00e9 13:2. Mt 10:40-42.) (1 R 17:17-24. H\u00e9 11:35.) (Ps 84:7; 116:11-12.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Un jour \u00c9lis\u00e9e passait par Sunem. Il y avait l\u00e0 une femme de distinction, qui le pressa d\u2019accepter \u00e0 manger. Et toutes les fois qu\u2019il passait, il se rendait chez elle pour manger.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.9","name":"2 Rois 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.7","name":"2 Rois 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.9","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:9","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Elle dit \u00e0 son mari: Voici, je sais que cet homme qui passe toujours chez nous est un saint homme de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.10","name":"2 Rois 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.8","name":"2 Rois 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.10","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:10","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Faisons une petite chambre haute avec des murs, et mettons-y pour lui un lit, une table, un si\u00e8ge et un chandelier, afin qu\u2019il s\u2019y retire quand il viendra chez nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.11","name":"2 Rois 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.9","name":"2 Rois 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.11","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:11","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e, \u00e9tant revenu \u00e0 Sunem, se retira dans la chambre haute et y coucha.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.12","name":"2 Rois 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.10","name":"2 Rois 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.12","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:12","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il dit \u00e0 Gu\u00e9hazi, son serviteur: Appelle cette Sunamite. Gu\u00e9hazi l\u2019appela, et elle se pr\u00e9senta devant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.13","name":"2 Rois 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.11","name":"2 Rois 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.13","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:13","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Et \u00c9lis\u00e9e dit \u00e0 Gu\u00e9hazi: Dis-lui: Voici, tu nous as montr\u00e9 tout cet empressement; que peut-on faire pour toi? Faut-il parler pour toi au roi ou au chef de l\u2019arm\u00e9e? Elle r\u00e9pondit: J\u2019habite au milieu de mon peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.14","name":"2 Rois 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.12","name":"2 Rois 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.14","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:14","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et il dit: Que faire pour elle? Gu\u00e9hazi r\u00e9pondit: Mais, elle n\u2019a point de fils, et son mari est vieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.15","name":"2 Rois 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.13","name":"2 Rois 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.15","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:15","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Et il dit: Appelle-la. Gu\u00e9hazi l\u2019appela, et elle se pr\u00e9senta \u00e0 la porte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.16","name":"2 Rois 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.14","name":"2 Rois 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.16","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:16","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e lui dit: A cette m\u00eame \u00e9poque, l\u2019ann\u00e9e prochaine, tu embrasseras un fils. Et elle dit: Non! Mon seigneur, homme de Dieu, ne trompe pas ta servante!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.17","name":"2 Rois 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.15","name":"2 Rois 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.17","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:17","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Cette femme devint enceinte, et elle enfanta un fils \u00e0 la m\u00eame \u00e9poque, l\u2019ann\u00e9e suivante, comme \u00c9lis\u00e9e lui avait dit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.18","name":"2 Rois 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.16","name":"2 Rois 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.18","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:18","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>L\u2019enfant grandit. Et un jour qu\u2019il \u00e9tait all\u00e9 trouver son p\u00e8re vers les moissonneurs,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.19","name":"2 Rois 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.17","name":"2 Rois 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.19","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:19","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>il dit \u00e0 son p\u00e8re: Ma t\u00eate! Ma t\u00eate! Le p\u00e8re dit \u00e0 son serviteur: Porte-le \u00e0 sa m\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.20","name":"2 Rois 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.18","name":"2 Rois 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.20","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:20","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Le serviteur l\u2019emporta et l\u2019amena \u00e0 sa m\u00e8re. Et l\u2019enfant resta sur les genoux de sa m\u00e8re jusqu\u2019\u00e0 midi, puis il mourut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.21","name":"2 Rois 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.19","name":"2 Rois 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.21","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:21","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Elle monta, le coucha sur le lit de l\u2019homme de Dieu, ferma la porte sur lui, et sortit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.22","name":"2 Rois 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.20","name":"2 Rois 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.22","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:22","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Elle appela son mari, et dit: Envoie-moi, je te prie, un des serviteurs et une des \u00e2nesses; je veux aller en h\u00e2te vers l\u2019homme de Dieu, et je reviendrai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.23","name":"2 Rois 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.21","name":"2 Rois 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.23","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:23","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Et il dit: Pourquoi veux-tu aller aujourd\u2019hui vers lui? Ce n\u2019est ni nouvelle lune ni sabbat. Elle r\u00e9pondit: Tout va bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.24","name":"2 Rois 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.22","name":"2 Rois 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.24","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:24","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Puis elle fit seller l\u2019\u00e2nesse, et dit \u00e0 son serviteur: M\u00e8ne et pars; ne m\u2019arr\u00eate pas en route sans que je te le dise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.25","name":"2 Rois 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.23","name":"2 Rois 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.25","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:25","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Elle partit donc et se rendit vers l\u2019homme de Dieu sur la montagne du Carmel. L\u2019homme de Dieu, l\u2019ayant aper\u00e7ue de loin, dit \u00e0 Gu\u00e9hazi, son serviteur: Voici cette Sunamite!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.26","name":"2 Rois 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.24","name":"2 Rois 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.26","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:26","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Maintenant, cours donc \u00e0 sa rencontre, et dis-lui: Te portes-tu bien? Ton mari et ton enfant se portent-ils bien? Elle r\u00e9pondit: Bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.27","name":"2 Rois 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.25","name":"2 Rois 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.27","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:27","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Et d\u00e8s qu\u2019elle fut arriv\u00e9e aupr\u00e8s de l\u2019homme de Dieu sur la montagne, elle embrassa ses pieds. Gu\u00e9hazi s\u2019approcha pour la repousser. Mais l\u2019homme de Dieu dit: Laisse-la, car son \u00e2me est dans l\u2019amertume, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel me l\u2019a cach\u00e9 et ne me l\u2019a point fait conna\u00eetre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.28","name":"2 Rois 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.26","name":"2 Rois 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.28","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:28","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Alors elle dit: Ai-je demand\u00e9 un fils \u00e0 mon seigneur? N\u2019ai-je pas dit: Ne me trompe pas?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.29","name":"2 Rois 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.27","name":"2 Rois 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.29","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:29","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Et \u00c9lis\u00e9e dit \u00e0 Gu\u00e9hazi: Ceins tes reins, prends mon b\u00e2ton dans ta main, et pars. Si tu rencontres quelqu\u2019un, ne le salue pas; et si quelqu\u2019un te salue, ne lui r\u00e9ponds pas. Tu mettras mon b\u00e2ton sur le visage de l\u2019enfant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.30","name":"2 Rois 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.28","name":"2 Rois 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.30","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:30","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>La m\u00e8re de l\u2019enfant dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant et ton \u00e2me est vivante! Je ne te quitterai point. Et il se leva et la suivit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.31","name":"2 Rois 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.29","name":"2 Rois 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.31","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:31","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Gu\u00e9hazi les avait devanc\u00e9s, et il avait mis le b\u00e2ton sur le visage de l\u2019enfant; mais il n\u2019y eut ni voix ni signe d\u2019attention. Il s\u2019en retourna \u00e0 la rencontre d\u2019\u00c9lis\u00e9e, et lui rapporta la chose, en disant: L\u2019enfant ne s\u2019est pas r\u00e9veill\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.32","name":"2 Rois 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.30","name":"2 Rois 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.32","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:32","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Lorsque \u00c9lis\u00e9e arriva dans la maison, voici, l\u2019enfant \u00e9tait mort, couch\u00e9 sur son lit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.33","name":"2 Rois 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.31","name":"2 Rois 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.33","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:33","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e entra et ferma la porte sur eux deux, et il pria l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.34","name":"2 Rois 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.32","name":"2 Rois 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.34","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:34","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Il monta, et se coucha sur l\u2019enfant; il mit sa bouche sur sa bouche, ses yeux sur ses yeux, ses mains sur ses mains, et il s\u2019\u00e9tendit sur lui. Et la chair de l\u2019enfant se r\u00e9chauffa.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.35","name":"2 Rois 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.33","name":"2 Rois 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.35","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:35","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e s\u2019\u00e9loigna, alla \u00e7\u00e0 et l\u00e0 par la maison, puis remonta et s\u2019\u00e9tendit sur l\u2019enfant. Et l\u2019enfant \u00e9ternua sept fois, et il ouvrit les yeux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.36","name":"2 Rois 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.34","name":"2 Rois 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.36","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:36","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e appela Gu\u00e9hazi, et dit: Appelle cette Sunamite. Gu\u00e9hazi l\u2019appela, et elle vint vers \u00c9lis\u00e9e, qui dit: Prends ton fils!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.37","name":"2 Rois 4:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.35","name":"2 Rois 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.37","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:37","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Elle alla se jeter \u00e0 ses pieds, et se prosterna contre terre. Et elle prit son fils, et sortit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.38","name":"2 Rois 4:38","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.36","name":"2 Rois 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.38","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:38","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.039,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La mort dans le pot<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 38-41: cf. 2 R 2:19-22. Ex 15:23-25. Ps 119:91.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e revint \u00e0 Guilgal, et il y avait une famine dans le pays. Comme les fils des proph\u00e8tes \u00e9taient assis devant lui, il dit \u00e0 son serviteur: Mets le grand pot, et fais cuire un potage pour les fils des proph\u00e8tes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.39","name":"2 Rois 4:39","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.37","name":"2 Rois 4:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.39","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:39","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>L\u2019un d\u2019eux sortit dans les champs pour cueillir des herbes; il trouva de la vigne sauvage et il y cueillit des coloquintes sauvages, plein son v\u00eatement. Quand il rentra, il les coupa en morceaux dans le pot o\u00f9 \u00e9tait le potage, car on ne les connaissait pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.40","name":"2 Rois 4:40","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.38","name":"2 Rois 4:38","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.40","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:40","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>On servit \u00e0 manger \u00e0 ces hommes; mais d\u00e8s qu\u2019ils eurent mang\u00e9 du potage, ils s\u2019\u00e9cri\u00e8rent: La mort est dans le pot, homme de Dieu! Et ils ne purent manger.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.41","name":"2 Rois 4:41","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.39","name":"2 Rois 4:39","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.41","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:41","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>\u00c9lis\u00e9e dit: Prenez de la farine. Il en jeta dans le pot, et dit: Sers \u00e0 ces gens, et qu\u2019ils mangent. Et il n\u2019y avait plus rien de mauvais dans le pot.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.42","name":"2 Rois 4:42","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.40","name":"2 Rois 4:40","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.42","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:42","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.043,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les vingt pains d\u2019orge<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 42-44: cf. Pr 3:9-10. Mt 14:14-21; 6:11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Un homme arriva de Baal-Schalischa. Il apporta du pain des pr\u00e9mices \u00e0 l\u2019homme de Dieu, vingt pains d\u2019orge, et des \u00e9pis nouveaux dans son sac. \u00c9lis\u00e9e dit: Donne \u00e0 ces gens, et qu\u2019ils mangent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.43","name":"2 Rois 4:43","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.41","name":"2 Rois 4:41","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.43","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:43","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>Son serviteur r\u00e9pondit: Comment pourrais-je en donner \u00e0 cent personnes? Mais \u00c9lis\u00e9e dit: Donne \u00e0 ces gens, et qu\u2019ils mangent; car ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: On mangera, et on en aura de reste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.44","name":"2 Rois 4:44","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.42","name":"2 Rois 4:42","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.44","label":"","reference":"2 Rois 4:44","prev_osis_id":"2Kgs.004.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Kgs.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Kgs.4.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>Il mit alors les pains devant eux; et ils mang\u00e8rent et en eurent de reste, selon la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4","name":"2 Rois 4","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.5.1","name":"2 Rois 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.43","name":"2 Rois 4:43","id":"fra-LSG:2Kgs.4.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb35b75b4.52032226');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb35b75b4.52032226\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb35b75b4.52032226","fums_js_incl